Author: nintentions
Text: the same thing happened to me when i started taking antipsychotics. i had to go off them because my anxiety was WORSE knowing i was gaining tons of weight. maybe there’s another medication out there that can help with your anxiety but have little effect on your appetite? lexapro has helped my anxiety and doesn’t seem to effect my weight if that helps
